          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "High purity platinium and gold foils,",
                "Pr2O3 and CeO2 oxide in powder form prepared by",
                "sedimentation onto Cu backing."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Pr2O3 and CeO2 samples were prepared by sedimentation",
                "onto 25 micron thick Cu backing. 30 - 60 minutes",
                "irradiations were applied. The prmary 3He energies were",
                "27.7 and 36.9 MeV. Primary proton energies were 20 and",
                "45 MeV. Monitor foils were used to check the beam",
                "current and beam energy.",
                "Irradiations were done at the CV28 and at COSY",
                "cyclotrons of Juelich.",
                "Gamma-spectara were recorded several times to",
                "check the half life and follow the decay. Detector",
                "sample distance was about 10 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DECAY-DATA": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Decay data were taken from R.B. Firestone, Table of",
                "Isotopes, CDROM version 1.0, 1996."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Measured cross sections were compared to the",
                "values of  model calculation STAPRE and EMPIRE."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The individual uncertainties of the cross sections and",
                "cross section ratios were combined in quadrature,",
                "taking into account the correlation of the data, to",
                "obtain an overall uncertainty of 9-31% and 9-50% for",
                "the cross sections and for the isomeric cross-section",
                "ratios, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
